Lizard Astrology
What is the Meaning of Lizard Falling on our Body?

We all must have seen lizards in our home, garden or somewhere else. It is a reptile and is very commonly seen almost everywhere, usually around human dwellings, hence many times they are also called home lizards. So, we are aware of how a lizard looks. Lizard falling on various parts of the human body have various meanings. In this blog, we will try to understand how lizard falling can bring good luck or bad luck to us. This is a type of prediction science like astrology, therefore commonly known as lizard astrology and Gowli Shasthram in part of Vedic Hindu Astrology. Falling lizards on various ‌parts of the body have a different meaning for both men and women. The falling of lizards and what they indicate is explained in “Muhurat Martand”. The shastra says every movement or fall of the lizard has some significance, and in 65 different body parts, the lizard falling would make good or bad predictions.

Here we will try to find out the effects of lizard falling for male and the effects of lizard falling for female as per Shastra.

There are two colours of lizards black and white that you will find in your home. While white lizards are believed to be good, black lizards are considered ‌inauspicious and bad. It makes “Tik Tik” sound that has different indications and prophecies to make in our daily lives. You will get to hear this sound in your house a few times a day. The sound may bring good to bad omens for you. Therefore, it is very important to check the house thoroughly before you buy, and also the land or property where the house is built.

You can consult our best astrologers on the phone or via chat to get a more detailed analysis of lizard sounds and lizard falling.

Business place, Big hall, Gambling place, Cities near the sea, school, school bag place, Information and Communication Department, Space Department, Education Department, Finance Department, Astrology, Business and Stage Talk.

Some Common Lizard Falling Effects

Lizard falling on the left hand leads to mental stress.

Lizard touches the fingers on the left hand leads to worries.

Lizard on right hand male brings favorable news.

If it falls on the left hand, it brings ‌unfavorable news.

A lizard drop on head indicates the person will be blessed with wealth, royalty with luxurious life.

If a lizard drop on head (on a rich person’s head), his wealth gradually diminishes.

If it falls on a sick bedridden rich person, then the suffering increases and can be death-like suffering.

If it falls on a sick bedridden poor person, it will be a reverse condition.

The falling of a lizard on the right ear increases the longevity of the native.

The falling of a lizard on the left ear improves one’s gain.

If it falls into the lip, the indication is of destroying wealth.

Lizard falling under the lip, a person’s lifestyle changes to a wealthy lifestyle.

If it falls above the throat, the person will be blessed with many good things, and he will destroy his enemy.

If it falls above the heart, it indicates death or death-like suffering.

If it falls between two knees, the person will possess good vehicles.

If it falls between the ankle and feet, it may kill the person’s wife.

Lizard Astrology for Male



Lizard falling on his face means financial profits.

If it falls on the left eye it is seen as a good indication.

If falls on the right eye, it indicates loss and failure.

Falling of a lizard on the forehead means separation.

The fall of the lizard on the mouth indicates a fear of awful health conditions.

Falling on a finger means expecting visitors and meeting old friends.

Falling on a man’s things means loss of clothing.

If it falls on the toe, it means physical illness.

Falling on a moustache means hurdles.

If it falls on the heel, it indicates an injury might occur.

If it falls on the left side nails, it creates wealth and if it falls on the right side you will increase your unnecessary expenses.

Falling on the left-side neck will bring out success whereas on the right side will increase enemies.

A lizard falling on the left leg of a male may incur some loss.

If it falls on your back foot it indicates you are travelling.

If it falls on foot it means a difficult time.

Lizard Astrology for Female



If a lizard falls on the right eye, it may create anxiety and mental stress.

If falls on the left eye, you will receive an abundance of love from your spouse.

A lizard falling on the upper lip means you may have a dispute.

If it falls on the lower lip, it indicates new good news will come.

If it falls on the backside, ‌you may get death news.

If it falls on your hands, you will gain financial profits.

If it falls on your shoulders, you may be adorned with ornaments.

A lizard falling on toes means you may have a male child.

What are the Remedies for Lizard Falling?

When you experience a lizard fall, irrespective of any body part:

You should immediately take a head bath.

Visit the nearest temple.

Light a diya in front of God.

Start reciting “Maha Mrityunjaya Mantra” to avoid negative thoughts.

If you live near Kanchipuram, visit the Varandaraja Perumal temple. It will protect you from all negative and harm.

Donate ’til’ to Sadhus if you are unable to visit the Varandaraja Perumal temple.

Consume Panchgavya to avoid evil effects.

Do not panic. The above remedies will help you get rid of any lizard doshas.
